cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper deals with deep neural network compression using pruning techniques, specifically for convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of a novel data-driven metric for evaluating the importance of channels in the network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Finally, the paper applies the proposed methodology to image datasets, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
